{"tid":954513,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"網吧日本人玩9旅客","createTime":"2018-12-24T15:58:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-26T13:50:59.000Z","uid":200895,"like":40,"dislike":428,"uniUserReply":89,"replies":[{"pid":"92686ec84e45bd2573a4113765e539c4b89be947","tid":954513,"uid":200895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T15:58:20.000Z","msg":"話說小弟今日去東京玩，以為一路順風，日本人nice爆接待，再入住某日本講國語夫婦youtuber推薦一網吧（haixxx cafe)，點知夜晚一入到網吧，一程4人想借宿一晚，每人比左成五千円去上房訓，發覺個陰9日本人將我地安排4人住一間房，而且間房面積只得幾十呎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。屌你老母，原來佢地係計人頭，而且陰9香港人唔識日文就扮幫手，實情就唔鍾意啲旅客，特登難為佢地 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n屌你好L彩我個fd即爆發，去櫃檯理論，先可以爭取翻兩人一間房。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以去日本真係要小心啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"129b5ce2cf6e2a08b67b149f7e82e9b40f16569e","tid":954513,"uid":60635,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T16:00:31.000Z","msg":"蝦你唔識野<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbd7aac8881eb731d797ef1f04469f18afd6754f","tid":954513,"uid":121146,"like":132,"dislike":6,"score":126,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T16:03:44.000Z","msg":"仲唔發毒誓以後唔去日本？"},{"pid":"8ad5b3ade7b3c07fd40478f3c2b3e8d7b5451c3b","tid":954513,"uid":40932,"like":346,"dislike":4,"score":342,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T16:04:21.000Z","msg":"去日本要住網吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb7947adaa3b3513fac77399b9a5291885c6b822","tid":954513,"uid":38143,"like":150,"dislike":1,"score":149,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T16:19: